// Loyalty counters ([CR#122.1e]): a planeswalker's loyalty IS its number of
// loyalty counters — read by `StatOf(_, Loyalty)`. A marker counter: it
// confers no continuous bearing of its own (the "0 loyalty → graveyard" SBA is
// engine-sba-breadth; placement on entry per [CR#209.1] is planeswalker work).
(
    name: "LoyaltyCounter",
    template: "loyalty counter",
    kinds: [Counter],
    body: Counter(name: "LoyaltyCounter"),
)
